Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.24,0:00:03.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The inside of one's heart is a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.90,0:00:05.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stars and snow shine around the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.80,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}With Ayumi's idea, the secret code is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is this person full of mysteries?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:13.17,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:15.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:47.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We went to watch Paul & Annie's animal show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:53.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There, we helped James Black{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}, a foreigner who'd been confused for somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:55.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But afterwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}James{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} went to get his car to take us to a restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.53,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and suddenly disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:07.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}leaving behind his keychain, stained with blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P & A?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It fell here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably a clue to the kidnapper that James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left behind for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left blood on the "P", "&" and "A" on the keychain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, first things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll take it to the station and check if it really is blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop by our police box tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:50.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we just knew what "P & A"\Nwas supposed to mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P and A make "pa"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a shop starting with "pa"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, like a bakery!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.30,0:03:06.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}pan-ya
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was in a hurry and trying to spell "pa",
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could've left blood on the first two letters of "Paul".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we have to separate the P and A to decipher this clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"P and A"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"P and A"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pink and red...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}aka-iro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pro wrestling and {\i1}anman{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,PC and access...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pistol and assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it could be "Parking Area"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the parking lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how are we supposed to know which parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he left us another clue inside the van at the parking lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought so too, and searched inside already. I didn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're not getting anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our best hope now is to assume they're still nearby,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and look for witnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's split up and ask around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See if anybody spotted two men with a foreigner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you find something, contact me with your Detective Badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm missing my Detective Badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you dropped it somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I showed it to James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just a little while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh! Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still has my badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.90,0:04:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.27,0:04:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I can track him with the badge's transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's currently at...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's 16 km north-northwest of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's traveling north on Ikumo Road along the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that speed, he must be in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ikumo Road?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Traveling north?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's what they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know what you're asking of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want us to set up a checkpoint on Ikumo Road at the Saitama border?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't tie up the roads on such flimsy information...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that foreigner's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:44.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? This is Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an accident in that area a moment ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Yumi's down there controlling traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can ask her to keep an eye out for the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A car carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an American of English descent, in his 50s or 60s, with glasses and a mustache,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,about 180 cm tall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll have Yumi stop any suspicious cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? The kidnappers might be armed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem. Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I will head out there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:25.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a slow day at the station anyhow,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and things always get interesting when that boy's involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:38.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go. Get your car, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones who can identify James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this seem fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left the parking lot, passed through this alley with two other men,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and got into a different car at the curb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've pricked his finger and created the code while he was walking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those men must've threatened him with a gun while he entered the parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he must've put the blood on the keychain while they weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he knew from the start that those two couldn't be trusted,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he left the message just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just have this feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:31.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that we're being played for fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you overthinking this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, did you see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The face of the guy in that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... it just sped by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:24.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:30.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:37.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mind if we go on ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We need this guy to verify a crime scene before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Nice work, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:59.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, he's just a lowlife who got high and trashed his girlfriend's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:12.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:15.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A foreigner... a foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aw, nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a foreigner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see even one foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's the car now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About 8 km away from here and still moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the transmitter's battery is dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How'd they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:40.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How did they get past us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that foreigner's got the badge, why can't we just call him and ask where he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnappers could hear it and they'd realize we can contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess our only hope is to solve the "P & A" riddle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:10:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a clue to where the car is headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it stands for "parfait and {\i1}anmitsu{\i0}", and they're going to a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe "perm and afro", and they're headed for a beauty parlor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you get serious, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Pelican and Sea Lion"! A zoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}ashika
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} likes animals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he wanted to tell us to try the zoo, he could've marked the "Animal" of "Animal Show"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it! That's what he meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well done, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know where James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnappers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are in a police car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't find them before dark, they'll get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi! How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find the kidnappers Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, where's the kidnappers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's telling me they're in a police car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A police car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the code James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} left us, "P & A".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was saying "police car".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? How does "P & A" mean "police car"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spell out the "&" in "P & A", and it'll become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"P & A"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"P" and "AND" and "A"...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,PA-N-DA...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coloring of a police car is black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, just like a panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true, police in Japan do call a squad car a "panda"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the guy who was kidnapped was American and came from England, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.21,0:12:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could a foreigner know slang used by Japanese police?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's not a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little white car with black trim would look even more like a panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in fact, for a foreigner, it'd make more sense for him to call one of {\i1}those{\i0} a panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's because James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the kidnapped man, grew up in London...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that it's got to be a police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,English police cars used to be painted the same way Japanese cars are today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coloring was first used in 1965 by the police in Lancashire, England.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police cars there were called "pandas", and the name gradually spread across England.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can still find the term in English dictionaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably isn't common slang among young people in Britain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:13:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but someone James{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s age would think of a police car as a "panda".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:07.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what era person are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I did let a police car pass without checking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't see a foreigner inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the officers in the car strike you as odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... There were two detectives in the back seat escorting a suspect with a coat over his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll make it to the mountains of Gunma before dawn, just like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a genius. Your plan is absolutely perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find it strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that that traffic cop was checking inside everybody's cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the cops are already onto us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep the gun at his throat in case anything goes down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we hit another suspicious checkpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we just force our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:47.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, w-w-what's the matter, Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already in Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've had the Saitama police set up a checkpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:57.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we don't need to chase the crooks...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi already checked the kidnappers' car once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they figure out we're after them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they could try to muscle their way through the next checkpoint, with him as a human shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when Yumi was checking the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that foreigner sat there silently without trying to alert her or escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a good possibility the kidnappers are armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:22.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they have a gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.10,0:15:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and they start shooting into traffic at the next checkpoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-They'll create a panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I've been trying to think of a way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to surround the kidnappers without attracting their notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before they can pull a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But something like that would take magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.78,0:15:46.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Detective Boys badge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.93,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry! I left my badge with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.23,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm about 500 meters away from your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:04.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got a plan, but I have to ask if you're up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.47,0:16:09.47,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Whether or not this crazy plan works...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,depends on how many cops you can get to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. What am I doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.53,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yumi? Are you following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just want to make up for letting them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:36.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Didn't you throw a party the other day with officers from the Saitama police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another red light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't want to attract attention with reckless driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once night falls, we'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's the cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like they caught on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, get the lead out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll use the hostage and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.67,0:17:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:35.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Takagi from the Metro Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you assist us in apprehending that kidnapper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drat. Talk about bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go along with him for now, and turn off when you get the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Good, they fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as we planned. Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, find a street and turn off...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with the Sunday driving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't turn left, turn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's another cop car on our right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then drop back! Slow down and get behind them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a cop car behind us too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:33.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,surrounded by cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goddamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:44.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How smart of you, irregulars...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:49.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I had better call you Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cops set us up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've still got a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.58,0:19:01.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When a commander makes a sign,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}all cars hit the brakes at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:15.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When the offenders are about to pick themselves up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:20.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}they will be under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's a little rough, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I've got to hand it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Cool Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, everybody! You saved the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easy job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't forget your end...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promse to get all the cute girls from Metro Police to the next mixer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.54,0:19:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy as long as Sato{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:50.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to James Black{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was here a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.18,0:20:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew there was something strange about that foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared before the police could question him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.62,0:20:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's definitely hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He seemed okay to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing that bugged me was his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Name? You mean "Black"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, "James".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:23.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? James Bond and James Dean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only think of positive associations for that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Professor James Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Napoleon of crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first name of Professor Moriarty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holmes' arch-nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess only a Sherlockian would think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like James is an uncommon name in Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.86,0:20:53.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But there's still the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}of that guy watching us from the other car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:21:00.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was one of the passengers in the busjacking incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:01.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he gave his name as Shuuichi Akai at the police station...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You always amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:40.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To leave a clue like that on the spur of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when did you notice they weren't real cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.05,0:22:51.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment they spoke. They used Japanese without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.42,0:22:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they were cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.93,0:22:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and knew that I was a foreigner who spoke Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.16,0:23:00.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would have started by confirming my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.97,0:23:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.57,0:23:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they were agents who already knew my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it turned out they were just common criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.92,0:23:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who mistook me for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, you gave me a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.33,0:23:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd cut your long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:20.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted a fresh start.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My sweetheart keeps rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.91,0:23:25.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You called me all the way out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're back on good terms with your so-called sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's hoping.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After rejecting me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make my sweetie pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with tears of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:54.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this bloodstain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.03,0:23:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.28,0:24:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today he's reasoning without falling asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:02.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:08.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.62,0:24:10.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How could this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,0:24:17.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Fish scale
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:27.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:23.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next Conan, a mysterious restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.46,0:24:25.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's one who gives you eel on rice whatever you ask for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.82,0:24:27.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What a great restaurant!
